Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊香和电蚊香都准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本以为过一会儿就会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有消失  深夜的  最上川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说一寸的蚊子有五寸的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是放弃好了  乖乖地去睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你这家伙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了无谓的杀生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么打  不管怎么打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年每年都无法绝迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已经不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…这个家已经不能住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能搬家了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为现在几点了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我安静地睡觉！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
