Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.52,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N38
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰棒上的中奖出现在下面了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么反应啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  又吃那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西是什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话晚饭都吃不下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来因为冰棒中个奖就这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是没长大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中奖写在下面可是超罕见的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面也好下面也罢  中奖就是中奖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃几次总会中奖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  做小鬼真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是中个奖就高兴成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是难得一见的超级稀有的东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就留在最后慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  博士你这不是完全没动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你白天吃了一堆零食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  你吃了储藏柜里多少零食啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部！  你把这个月的份全部吃掉了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没夸奖你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为是阪本叫我吃的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为阪本说夏天食物容易变质的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个和那个是两回事好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还说点心是装在另一个胃里的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是过午休的OL吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么什么都当真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全是被冤枉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说黑还是白  我就是纯白啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本你是纯黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  那是天生就长成这样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再说下去也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士的草莓果汁我就没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃零食了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰棒中的奖我送给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会好好吃蔬菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你应该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把名乃的发条取下来的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只允许你这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再犯  就一个月不准你吃零食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有种现在给她的话  就会被她混过去的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先把发条取下来再喝草莓果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就背对着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}没中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手是没中奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么东西都给我装啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有夸你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为博士你太随意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请三思而后行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有在听啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:29.91,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(1000,0)\an8}还算过得去的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句话时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去检索的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可能会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美绪  正找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐正好有点急事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你代替我去街道会的摊位帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这种事让妈妈去做就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和朋友去踢藤球了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看  有一万円的打工费哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:41.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}街道会大福展销会 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一万円的打工费真诱人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正很闲  就去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么超可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.24,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,300)\fad(0,600)}日\N常\N之\N39
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么鬼东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要陷入这种困境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:19:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且街道会的活动居然是两个人在街边卖大福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丢脸啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丢脸了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路人都用可悲的眼神望着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能招来客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是吉祥物的大福君？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有眼睛也没有嘴  只有一张白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都已经不是大福君了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是大福啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大福展销会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么展销会啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全出局了呢  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  很痛的啦  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  下面没有戴护具啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面没有戴护具啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…你们  给我住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气了  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样破坏大福的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的示范
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把这个取下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不想请打工的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻站着  去帮我看摊子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  为了一万円的打工费  我就忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:21:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糯米粉  小红豆  和三盆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:21:00.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}和三盆：一种上等砂糖，产于香川县、德岛县等地，经常用于和式甜点的制作。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好想家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这些真的卖得出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然摆得很整齐的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  这个一个多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说到底是多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  大福一个多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和三盆的不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不干呢  我才不用草莓什么的来做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免费赠送
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  LUCKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
