Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.03,0:23:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东云家今天也很和平
