Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:03.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我是不是坠入爱河了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.57,0:01:06.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}24小时满脑子都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:07.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}意识不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:10.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}觉得与平时不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:09.57,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}觉\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:13.28,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:12.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N个\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:16.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}难道  不对  是单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N情\N相\N悦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:18.50,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟了  视线和他对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:22.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}什么什么  这种忐忑心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:28.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思考回路乱成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.46,0:01:34.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那种事情  我可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:38.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感觉都要发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:42.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}急转直下的我的爱慕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:45.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}眨眼间  脸像着火般变得通红
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怎怎怎么可能  我的手居然在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这是所谓的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:53.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不不不不好了  说话咬到舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟糕的沉默  我语无伦次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:58.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想知道  你对我的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:57.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}你\N对\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:01.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}初恋！  在平日的上学路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:07.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飞翔般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.57,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
